---
<ServicePage
  title="Smile Design in Bayside, Queens NY | Thrive Dental"
  description="Custom smile design in Bayside, Queens NY. We combine veneers, whitening, Invisalign®, and more to create your perfect smile. Expert cosmetic dentists. Call (718) 225-6677."
  category="Cosmetic Dentistry"
  categoryHref="/services/cosmetic-dentistry"
  h1="Smile Design in Bayside, Queens"
  subtitle="A smile makeover is more than cosmetics — it's a fully personalized plan built around your face, goals, and lifestyle. We combine treatments artistically to create a result that's uniquely yours."
  heroImg={heroImg}
  heroImgPosition="45%"
  overviewTitle="Your smile, designed from the ground up."
  overviewText="Smile design — sometimes called a smile makeover — is the process of combining multiple cosmetic and restorative treatments to completely transform how your smile looks and functions. The difference between a generic cosmetic treatment and a true smile design is planning: we map your facial proportions, analyze your bite, assess gum symmetry, and use digital design tools to build a virtual preview of your result before any tooth is touched. You see your new smile first. Then we build it."
  overviewExtra="Patients in Bayside, Whitestone, Fresh Meadows, and throughout Northern Queens who are serious about their smile come to Thrive Dental because we approach cosmetic dentistry as a discipline, not an upsell. Our smile design consultations are comprehensive — we photograph your face from multiple angles, take a full digital scan with iTero, and use smile design software to model your result in proportion to your face shape and skin tone. Common combinations include teeth whitening + veneers for patients who want dramatic color and shape changes, Invisalign + whitening + bonding for alignment-focused cases, or full arch veneers for complete transformations. Whatever the combination, every element is planned to look like it belongs — because the best cosmetic dentistry is invisible as dentistry."
  benefits={[
    {
      icon: `<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/>`,
      title: 'See It Before We Build It',
      desc: 'Digital smile design shows you the result before any tooth is touched. You approve the design — then we execute it.',
    },
    {
      icon: `<path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>`,
      title: 'Fully Personalized',
      desc: 'No cookie-cutter templates. Every element — shade, shape, length, gum line — is chosen to complement your specific face.',
    },
    {
      icon: `<path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/>`,
      title: 'Function + Aesthetics',
      desc: 'A great smile design always addresses bite balance and long-term durability — not just what it looks like on day one.',
    },
  ]}
  faq={[
    {
      q: 'What is included in a smile design consultation?',
      a: 'We take clinical photos, a digital scan, and facial measurements. Using smile design software, we create a digital mockup showing your new smile. We then discuss which treatments achieve that result, the treatment sequence, timeline, and total investment.',
    },
    {
      q: 'How long does a full smile makeover take?',
      a: 'It depends on which treatments are involved. A whitening and bonding combination can be done in 2–3 visits over a few weeks. A comprehensive makeover involving Invisalign and veneers may take 12–18 months.',
    },
    {
      q: 'Can I choose the shade of my new smile?',
      a: 'Absolutely. Shade selection is one of the most important parts of the design process. We use a shade guide along with your skin tone and personal preferences to select a shade that looks naturally beautiful — not artificially bright.',
    },
    {
      q: 'Does smile design address function too?',
      a: 'Always. An ideal result is one where your bite is balanced, your gums are healthy, and your teeth can withstand normal chewing forces. We never sacrifice function for aesthetics.',
    },
    {
      q: 'How much does a smile makeover cost in Bayside, NY?',
      a: 'Costs vary widely depending on the treatments involved. We provide a detailed cost breakdown at your consultation and offer financing through CareCredit with flexible monthly payment options.',
    },
  ]}
